  <div class="ct">
  
<p>This POV seems to be saying that marriage is needed to keep straight people from accidentally having kids outside of it.</p>
<p>Ignoring the obvious issue that a) it doesn't stop that, and b) huh? It exists solely to keep things from happening without it?</p>
